        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">DBNs, mentioned above, are actually a stack of Boltzmann Machines (surrounded by VAEs). They can be chained together (when one NN trains another) and can be used to generate data by already learned pattern.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
